            <title>[PIG-446] Problem when schema contains more columns that actual data</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-446</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Script:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;#8211; extra1 and extra2 are not present in the data&lt;br/&gt;
A = load &apos;data&apos; as (name, age: int, gpa, extra1, extra2);&lt;br/&gt;
B = limit A 10;&lt;br/&gt;
